OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775178189
OL,3,CUK to chair global meeting on Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz as Trump speech spikes oil
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FThe UK will chair a meeting of more
OL,8,Fthan 30 countries on Thursday to
OL,9,Fdiscuss reopening the Strait of
OL,10,FHormuz, after US President Donald
OL,11,FTrump's speech saw oil prices rise by
OL,12,F4%.
OL,14,FTrump said the US military would hit
OL,15,FIran "extremely hard over the next two
OL,16,Fto three weeks" during his first
OL,17,Fprimetime address since the war began.
OL,19,F"We're going to bring them back to the
OL,20,FStone Ages, where they belong," he
OL,21,Fadded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
