OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775178189
OL,3,CUK to chair global meeting on Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz as Trump speech spikes oil
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FOil prices rose more than 4% and Asian
OL,8,Fstocks fell immediately after, with
OL,9,FBrent crude oil - the international
OL,10,Fstandard - jumping to $106.22 (#80.44)
OL,11,Fper barrel.
OL,13,FUK Foreign Secretary Yvette Cooper
OL,14,Fwill chair a virtual meeting with 35
OL,15,Fcountries, to assess "all viable
OL,16,Fdiplomatic and political measures"
OL,17,Fthat could fully reopen the Strait of
OL,18,FHormuz, a vital waterway through which
OL,19,Fa fifth of the world's oil passes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
