OL,7,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FCountries like the UK, Italy, France,
OL,13,FGermany, Canada, Japan and the United
OL,14,FArab Emirates have signed a statement
OL,15,Fdemanding Iran stop its attempts to
OL,16,Fblock the strait.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/20
