OL,3,CUK to chair global meeting on Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz as Trump speech spikes oil
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FMeanwhile Iran's armed forces said on
OL,8,FThursday the war would continue until
OL,9,Fthe enemy's "surrender and permanent
OL,10,Fregret", according to regime's semi-
OL,11,Fofficial Tasnim news agency.
OL,13,FIsrael said it had intercepted Iranian
OL,14,Fmissiles early on Thursday morning,
OL,15,Fwhile Iraq warned US citizens not to
OL,16,Ftravel to the country and to leave if
OL,17,Falready there.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/20
