OL,3,CUK to chair global meeting on Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz as Trump speech spikes oil
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FAn estimated 15% of Lebanon's
OL,8,Fpopulation have been displaced by
OL,9,FIsraeli attacks and evacuation orders,
OL,10,Fhumanitarian agencies have said,
OL,11,Fdescribing it as "unprecedented".
OL,13,FTrump's primetime address sees oil
OL,14,Fprices spike
OL,16,FThe US president made his first
OL,17,Fprimetime address since the war began
OL,18,Fon Wednesday evening - and notably did
OL,19,Fnot repeat his claims that
OL,20,Fnegotiations with Iran are underway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
