OL,3,CUK to chair global meeting on Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz as Trump speech spikes oil
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,F"America, as it has been for five
OL,8,Fyears under my presidency, is winning,
OL,9,Fand now winning bigger than ever
OL,10,Fbefore," the Trump said, adding that
OL,11,Fthe military would "finish the job"
OL,12,Fand finish it "very fast".
OL,14,FThe president didn't mention the
OL,15,Fpossibility of sending US ground
OL,16,Ftroops into Iran, and also did not
OL,17,Freference Nato, the trans-Atlantic
OL,18,Falliance he has railed against for not
OL,19,Fjoining in efforts to reopen the
OL,20,FStrait of Hormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
