OL,3,CUK to chair global meeting on Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz as Trump speech spikes oil
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FHe threatened Iran's electric
OL,8,Fgenerating plants if a deal between
OL,9,Fthe countries is not made.
OL,11,F"We are going to hit (Iran) extremely
OL,12,Fhard over the next two to three weeks.
OL,13,FWe're going to bring them back to the
OL,14,FStone Ages, where they belong," Trump
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FThe comments were later repeated by US
OL,18,FDefence Secretary Pete Hegseth, who
OL,19,Fwrote on X: "Back to the Stone Age."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
