OL,3,CUK to chair global meeting on Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz as Trump speech spikes oil
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FOil prices were sharply higher after
OL,8,FTrump's remarks, with Brent crude oil
OL,9,Fsoaring above $106 (#80.28) a barrel.
OL,11,FSince the speech, Trump's Stone Age
OL,12,Fcomments have been heavily criticised,
OL,13,Fwith the Council on American`Islamic
OL,14,FRelations (CAIR) describing them as
OL,15,F"anti-Muslim, racist, and
OL,16,Fdehumanising".
OL,18,FIran denies talks of a ceasefire
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/20
