OL,4,Cof Hormuz as Trump speech spikes oil
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FA spokesperson for Iran's armed forces
OL,8,Fsaid on Thursday the war will continue
OL,9,Funtil the "enemy's surrender and
OL,10,Fpermanent regret" following Trump's
OL,11,Fspeech.
OL,13,FThey also warned of further
OL,14,F"destructive actions" against the US
OL,15,Fin a statement published via state
OL,16,Fnews.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/20
