OL,3,CUK to chair global meeting on Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz as Trump speech spikes oil
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FBefore Trump's address, Iran's
OL,8,FPresident Masoud Pezeshkian said Iran
OL,9,Fwould endure US aggression, noting
OL,10,Fthat the countries had a choice
OL,11,Fbetween "confrontation and engagement".
OL,13,F"Today, the world stands at
OL,14,Fcrossroads. Continuing along the path
OL,15,Fof confrontation is more costly and
OL,16,Ffutile than ever before," Pezeshkian
OL,17,Fwrote in an open letter on X.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
