OL,3,CUK to chair global meeting on Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz as Trump speech spikes oil
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,F"The choice between confrontation and
OL,8,Fengagement is both real and
OL,9,Fconsequential; its outcome will shape
OL,10,Fthe future for generations to come.
OL,11,FThroughout its millennia of proud
OL,12,Fhistory, Iran has outlasted many
OL,13,Faggressors.
OL,15,F"All that remains of them are
OL,16,Ftarnished names in history, while Iran
OL,17,Fendures - resilient, dignified, and
OL,18,Fproud."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
