OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FOn Wednesday, Trump said in a post on
OL,8,FTruth Social that "Iran's new regime
OL,9,Fpresident" had asked the US for a
OL,10,Fceasefire.
OL,12,FAn Iranian foreign ministry spokesman
OL,13,Fdenied the claim, calling Trump's
OL,14,Fcomments "false and baseless".
OL,16,FCooper to chair global Strait of
OL,17,FHormuz discussion
