OL,4,Cof Hormuz as Trump speech spikes oil
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FCooper will assess "all viable
OL,8,Fdiplomatic and political measures" the
OL,9,FUK and allied countries can take to
OL,10,F"restore freedom of navigation" in the
OL,11,FStrait of Hormuz in a virtual meeting
OL,12,Fon Thursday, UK Prime Minister Keir
OL,13,FStarmer said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/20
