OL,3,CUK to chair global meeting on Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz as Trump speech spikes oil
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FIranian attacks on commercial ships,
OL,8,Fand the threat of more, have halted
OL,9,Fnearly all traffic in the waterway
OL,10,Fthat connects the Persian Gulf to the
OL,11,Frest of the globe's oceans, shutting a
OL,12,Fcritical path for the world's flow of
OL,13,Foil and sending petroleum prices
OL,14,Fsoaring.
OL,16,FNo country is willing to try and open
OL,17,Fthe strait by force as the conflict
OL,18,Fcontinues, and Iran can attack vessels
OL,19,Fwith anti-ship missiles, drones,
OL,20,Fattack craft and mines.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
