OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775178189
OL,3,CUK to chair global meeting on Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz as Trump speech spikes oil
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FThe meeting is considered to be the
OL,8,Ffirst step after 35 countries signed a
OL,9,Fstatement demanding Iran stop its
OL,10,Fattempts to block the strait and
OL,11,Fpledged to "contribute to appropriate
OL,12,Fefforts to ensure safe passage"
OL,13,Fthrough the waterway.
OL,15,FIt will be followed by "working-level
OL,16,Fmeetings" of officials to hammer out
OL,17,Fdetails, Starmer said.
OL,26,@xD@IO]
