OL,4,Cof Hormuz as Trump speech spikes oil
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FThe PM said resuming shipping "will
OL,8,Fnot be easy," and will require "a
OL,9,Funited front of military strength and
OL,10,Fdiplomatic activity" alongside
OL,11,Fpartnership with the maritime industry.
OL,13,FEnergy crisis continues worldwide
OL,15,FSouth Korea's President Lee Jae Myung
OL,16,Fhas urged legislators to approve a
OL,17,F26.2 trillion won (about #13 billion)
OL,18,Fsupplementary budget to mitigate the
OL,19,F"extraordinary" energy crisis due to
OL,20,Fthe war.
