OL,3,CUK to chair global meeting on Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz as Trump speech spikes oil
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FLee proposed using the funds to
OL,8,Fbankroll government-set price caps on
OL,9,Foil, which the country has reinstated
OL,10,Ffor the first time in three decades,
OL,11,Fand provide tiered subsidies of up to
OL,12,F600,000 won (about #300) to low and
OL,13,Fmiddle-income households struggling
OL,14,Fwith fuel costs.
OL,16,F"Even if the war ends tomorrow, it
OL,17,Fwould take considerable time to
OL,18,Frestore destroyed infrastructure in
OL,19,Fthe Middle East and restore the flow
OL,20,Fof supplies to previous levels," Lee
OL,21,Fsaid.
