OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FFuel prices in Thailand soared on
OL,8,FThursday for the second time this week
OL,9,Fafter the government further cut
OL,10,Fsubsidies, increasing diesel prices by
OL,11,F12%.
OL,13,FJet fuel supplies could be disrupted
OL,14,Fin May and June if the war in Iran
OL,15,Fdoes not come to an end, Ryanair boss
OL,16,FMichael O'Leary warned after Trump's
OL,17,Fspeech - and the UK could be hit
OL,18,Fparticularly hard.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
