OL,3,CUK to chair global meeting on Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz as Trump speech spikes oil
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,F"Of all the European countries at the
OL,8,Fmoment, the one that is most
OL,9,Fvulnerable is the UK because of the
OL,10,Fmarket share that the Kuwaitis have
OL,11,Fhere," O'Leary said on Thursday.
OL,13,F"There could be a surplus of jet A-1
OL,14,Ffuel in the Middle East, but you have
OL,15,Fstill got to ship it to Europe and we
OL,16,Fdon't know when or how that happens."
